502
00:26:37.621 --> 00:26:39.465
-No. I...
-Electra: Yes.

503
00:26:39.498 --> 00:26:40.924
It was definitely you.

504
00:26:40.958 --> 00:26:42.852
I remember because it was
the weekend that Hollis

505
00:26:42.876 --> 00:26:44.978
